@startuml RegisterUserAltEmailExists
title UC 2.1.1 - Registracija (Alt: Email već postoji)

actor Gost as U
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "Backend API (Express)" as BE
database "MySQL" as DB

U -> FE: Unosi podatke
U -> FE: Klik na "Kreiraj nalog"
FE -> BE: POST /auth/register
BE -> DB: Provera emaila
DB --> BE: Email već postoji
BE --> FE: 409 Conflict (email exists)
FE -> U: Prikaz poruke o grešci
@enduml
